      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="10%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">On the next page is a mock-up of a Marine VHF radio.</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="20%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">Turn it on, and turn the &quot;squelch&quot; so that the noise has just gone.</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="26%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">Keep a "Listening Watch" for a distress call.</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="32%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">Silence the alarm, listen to the message, and note down Jack's exact position.</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="38%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">For example: 5544'33.22&quot;N 233'44.55&quot;W</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="44%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">Follow the pop-up link when ready.</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="50%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">Drag/Scroll/Zoom the map to find the Captain.</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="05%" y="56%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="left" class="child">You can reload to restart!</text>
      <text id="GoText" x="50%" y="70%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle" class="child" style="font-size:4px;">Volume up! and Click the screen to proceed...</text>
